{"tid":127014,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺淨係識怨自己嘅人係唔抵可憐","createTime":"2017-02-19T18:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T05:53:29.000Z","uid":33637,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d46419e25b044c79f9650b41726d2502d5c3a61","tid":127014,"uid":33637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:47:16.000Z","msg":"其實依啲說話我係想同自己講<br />\n<br />\n一味淨係識得怨自己究竟有咩用<br />\n<br />\n世界唔會因為你嘅負能量而對你好咗<br />\n<br />\n可能只會更加孤立到自己<br />\n<br />\n有時係度諗 點解自己咁冇用讀書又差又溝唔到女又冇目標 搞到係咁放負<br />\n<br />\n放完又好似冇事咁繼續做返同一樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n自己一日唔肯去改變 一日都會係咁<br />\n<br />\n其實真係唔抵可憐 你期望人地可以點幫到你?<br />\n<br />\n唔係話要變咩正能量JJ 有時人有情緒都好正常<br />\n<br />\n但係未盡力又怨自己點點點嗰d有咩意思啫<br />\n<br />\n今日起立定決心去盡力做好每一樣嘢吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for too long didn&lsquo;t read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />篇嘢希望比到各位巴絲睇到之餘都可以告誡下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5be36d88dd4596d69bf2a491651a21bd077054","tid":127014,"uid":66926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:54:15.000Z","msg":"不逆詐，不億不信，不念舊惡，不怨天，不尤人"},{"pid":"594438e2b276835c3b1046d135e35ef5b7721a08","tid":127014,"uid":33637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:06:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不逆詐，不億不信，不念舊惡，不怨天，不尤人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8701ede7081afeb18840ed8147224a5c063074","tid":127014,"uid":26020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:46:06.000Z","msg":"加油巴打 多謝你嘅提醒！"},{"pid":"b6299cdd2322e802139fa63e514f815697ff2145","tid":127014,"uid":33637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油巴打 多謝你嘅提醒！</blockquote><br />\n希望你同我都改變到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 